{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-368","title":"火山爆发","sectionId":"chapter-16","sectionTitle":"天文地理有规律","pageStart":1795,"pageEnd":1799,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":27,"duplicateEntryCount":12,"pages":[{"number":1795,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"368 火山爆发"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"active volcano 活火山","headword":"active volcano"},{"type":"entry","text":"extinct volcano 死火山","headword":"extinct volcano"},{"type":"entry","text":"volcano activity 火山活动","headword":"volcano activity"},{"type":"entry","text":"volcanic eruption 火山爆发","headword":"volcanic eruption"},{"type":"entry","text":"volcanic earthquake 火山地震","headword":"volcanic earthquake"},{"type":"entry","text":"volcanic dome 火山丘","headword":"volcanic dome"},{"type":"entry","text":"volcanic cloud 火山云","headword":"volcanic cloud"},{"type":"entry","text":"volcanic gas 火山气体","headword":"volcanic gas"},{"type":"entry","text":"supervolcano [ˈsuːpəvɒlkeɪnəʊ]","headword":"supervolcano"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.超级火山"},{"type":"entry","text":"composite volcano 复式火山","headword":"composite volcano"}]},{"number":1796,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"basin-shaped [ˌbeɪsn ˈʃeɪpt]","headword":"basin-shaped"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.盆状的"},{"type":"entry","text":"bowl-shaped crater 碗形的火山口","headword":"bowl-shaped crater"},{"type":"entry","text":"formation of cone 火山口的形成","headword":"formation of cone"},{"type":"entry","text":"ejected material 喷射出来的物质","headword":"ejected material"},{"type":"entry","text":"blast [blɑːst]","headword":"blast"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.爆炸；气浪，冲击波"},{"type":"note","text":"◎atomic blast原子弹爆炸"},{"type":"entry","text":"blob [blɒb]","headword":"blob"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.一滴，一团"}]},{"number":1797,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"bomb [bɒm]","headword":"bomb"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.火山口喷出的大堆球状熔岩"},{"type":"entry","text":"lava flow 熔岩流","headword":"lava flow"},{"type":"entry","text":"fire ball 火球","headword":"fire ball"},{"type":"entry","text":"crater lake 火山湖","headword":"crater lake"},{"type":"entry","text":"ash [æʃ]","headword":"ash"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.火山灰；灰烬"},{"type":"note","text":"◎burn to ashes烧成灰"},{"type":"entry","text":"ash particle 灰烬微粒","headword":"ash particle"},{"type":"entry","text":"lapillus [ləˈpɪləs]","headword":"lapillus"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.火山砾"},{"type":"entry","text":"fumarole [ˈfjuːmərəʊl]","headword":"fumarole"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.火山喷气孔"},{"type":"entry","text":"slag [slæɡ]","headword":"slag"}]},{"number":1798,"blocks":[{"type":"definition","text":"n.矿渣；火山岩渣"},{"type":"entry","text":"cinder cone 火山渣形成的圆锥体","headword":"cinder cone"},{"type":"entry","text":"destroy [dɪˈstrɔɪ]","headword":"destroy"},{"type":"definition","text":"v.毁坏，破坏；摧残"},{"type":"note","text":"◎destroy a village摧毁村庄"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 1"},{"type":"example","text":"A：What's the harm of volcano? （火山的危害是什么？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：It causes great bad impact on the global climate and its ash can"},{"type":"text","text":"cause respiratory diseases.（火山会对全球的气候造成巨大的不良影"},{"type":"text","text":"响，并且火山灰会引起呼吸道疾病。）"},{"type":"section","text":"Conversation 2"}]},{"number":1799,"blocks":[{"type":"example","text":"A：How does volcanic eruption form? （火山喷发是怎样形成"},{"type":"text","text":"的？）"},{"type":"example","text":"B：Originally, the interior of the earth is filled with hot magma.Under"},{"type":"text","text":"tremendous pressure, the hot magma will break through the earth's crust and"},{"type":"text","text":"spout out, thus the volcano eruption forms. （起初，地球内部充满热岩"},{"type":"text","text":"浆。在巨大的压力下，热岩浆会冲出地壳，喷涌而出，火山喷发便由"},{"type":"text","text":"此形成。）"}]}]}